    <stitle>530 and DT-466/408 Diesel Engine Service (1994) - TURBOCHARGERS - DISASSEMBLY</stitle>
    <svcman/>
    <svcproc svcproctype="proctype" graphiccount="9">
        <title>DISASSEMBLY</title>
        <para>Mark the compressor housing location to the back plate to aid in reassembly. Refer to
            <emph type="bold">FIGURE
                <hotlnk xrefid="ef1050214">2.14</hotlnk>
            </emph>
            .
        </para>
        <specpara>
            <note>
                <para>Reorientation of compressor housing on vehicle will damage compression housing O-Ring.</para>
            </note>
        </specpara>
        <specpara>
            <note>
                <para>The disassemble procedure is the same for the wastegate and non wastegate turbochargers except
                    where noted.
                </para>
            </note>
        </specpara>
        <para>Disassemble turbocharger as follows:</para>
        <step1>
            <para count="1">Remove two (2) hose clamps on the hose connecting the turbine side of the turbocharger to
                the wastegate actuator. Remove hose.
                <emph type="bold">If Equipped.</emph>
            </para>
        </step1>
        <step1>
            <para count="1">Remove six (6) bolts securing compressor housing to backplate. Remove clamps. Refer to
                <emph type="bold">FIGURE
                    <hotlnk xrefid="ef1050215">2.15</hotlnk>
                </emph>
                .
            </para>
            <figure id="ef1050214" figsize="col-wide">
                <graphic id="cg12005" filename="../figcg1/CG12005.webp" type="webp"/>
                <caption>FIGURE 2.14.</caption>
            </figure>
            <figure id="ef1050215" figsize="col-wide">
                <graphic id="eg3112" filename="../figeg3/EG3112.webp" type="webp"/>
                <caption>FIGURE 2.15.</caption>
                <calloutgroup>
                    <callout1>1. Compressor Housing</callout1>
                    <callout1>2. Clamps With Mounting Bolts</callout1>
                </calloutgroup>
            </figure>
        </step1>
        <step1>
            <para count="1">Remove compressor housing from backplate and O-Ring.</para>
        </step1>
        <step1>
            <para count="1">Mark turbine and center housing.</para>
        </step1>
        <step1>
            <para count="1">Remove four (4) bolts securing center housing to turbine housing (
                <emph type="bold">FIGURE
                    <hotlnk xrefid="ef1050216">2.16</hotlnk>
                </emph>
                )
            </para>
            <specpara>
                <note>
                    <para>If turbocharger is equipped with a wastegate, perform steps 6, 7 and 8. If turbocharger is not
                        equipped with a wastegate, proceed onto step 9.
                    </para>
                </note>
            </specpara>
        </step1>
        <step1>
            <para count="1">Remove six (6) bolts securing wastegate housing to turbine housing. Remove housing. Refer to
                <emph type="bold">FIGURE
                    <hotlnk xrefid="ef1050217">2.17</hotlnk>
                </emph>
                .
            </para>
            <figure id="ef1050216" figsize="col-wide">
                <graphic id="eg3095" filename="../figeg3/EG3095.webp" type="webp"/>
                <caption>FIGURE 2.16.</caption>
                <calloutgroup>
                    <callout1>1. Turbine Housing</callout1>
                    <callout1>2. Center Housing</callout1>
                </calloutgroup>
            </figure>
            <figure id="ef1050217" figsize="col-wide">
                <graphic id="eg3096" filename="../figeg3/EG3096.webp" type="webp"/>
                <caption>FIGURE 2.17.</caption>
                <calloutgroup>
                    <callout1>1. Wastegate Housing</callout1>
                    <callout1>2. Turbine Housing</callout1>
                    <callout1>3. Wastegate Housing Mounting Bolts (6)</callout1>
                </calloutgroup>
            </figure>
        </step1>
        <step1>
            <para count="1">Remove retaining clip to disengage wastegate actuator arm (
                <emph type="bold">3, FIGURE
                    <hotlnk xrefid="ef1050218">2.18</hotlnk>
                </emph>
                ).
            </para>
        </step1>
        <step1>
            <para count="1">Remove three (3) bolts securing wastegate actuator arm bracket to center housing. Remove
                actuator bracket arm. Refer to
                <emph type="bold">FIGURE
                    <hotlnk xrefid="ef1050218">2.18</hotlnk>
                </emph>
                .
            </para>
            <specpara>
                <note>
                    <para>Compressor wheel must be turned clockwise when removing from turbine shaft. If compressor
                        wheel is turned counterclockwise, threads located on the shaft will be damaged and turbine can
                        not be reused.
                    </para>
                </note>
            </specpara>
        </step1>
        <step1>
            <para count="1">Disassemble center housing as follows:</para>
            <step2>
                <para count="1">Clamp turbocharger center housing in a vise and separate compressor impeller from
                    turbine shaft (
                    <emph type="bold">FIGURE
                        <hotlnk xrefid="ef1050219">2.19</hotlnk>
                    </emph>
                    ).
                </para>
            </step2>
            <step2>
                <para count="1">Remove four (4) bolts securing center housing backplate (
                    <emph type="bold">FIGURE
                        <hotlnk xrefid="ef1050220">2.20</hotlnk>
                    </emph>
                    ).
                </para>
                <figure id="ef1050218" figsize="col-wide">
                    <graphic id="eg3097" filename="../figeg3/EG3097.webp" type="webp"/>
                    <caption>FIGURE 2.18.</caption>
                    <calloutgroup>
                        <callout1>1. Wastegate Actuator Arm</callout1>
                        <callout1>2. Wastegate Bracket Mounting Bolts (3)</callout1>
                        <callout1>3. Retaining Clip</callout1>
                    </calloutgroup>
                </figure>
                <figure id="ef1050219" figsize="col-wide">
                    <graphic id="eg3099" filename="../figeg3/EG3099.webp" type="webp"/>
                    <caption>FIGURE 2.19.</caption>
                    <calloutgroup>
                        <callout1>1. Impeller Wheel</callout1>
                        <callout1>2. Compressor Housing Backplate</callout1>
                        <callout1>3. Turbine Wheel</callout1>
                    </calloutgroup>
                </figure>
                <figure id="ef1050220" figsize="col-wide">
                    <graphic id="eg3101" filename="../figeg3/EG3101.webp" type="webp"/>
                    <caption>FIGURE 2.20.</caption>
                    <calloutgroup>
                        <callout1>1. Compressor Housing Backplate</callout1>
                        <callout1>2. Compressor Housing Backplate Bolts</callout1>
                    </calloutgroup>
                </figure>
            </step2>
            <step2>
                <para count="1">Remove O-Ring from center housing (
                    <emph type="bold">FIGURE
                        <hotlnk xrefid="ef1050221">2.21</hotlnk>
                    </emph>
                    ).
                </para>
            </step2>
        </step1>
        <step1>
            <para count="1">. Push turbine shaft wheel from center housing.</para>
        </step1>
        <step1>
            <para count="1">. Remove two bearings, spacer and piston ring from center housing (
                <emph type="bold">FIGURE
                    <hotlnk xrefid="ef1050222">2.22</hotlnk>
                </emph>
                ).
            </para>
            <figure id="ef1050221" figsize="col-wide">
                <graphic id="eg3107" filename="../figeg3/EG3107.webp" type="webp"/>
                <caption>FIGURE 2.21.</caption>
                <calloutgroup>
                    <callout1>1. O-Ring</callout1>
                    <callout1>2. Center Housing</callout1>
                </calloutgroup>
            </figure>
            <figure id="ef1050222" figsize="col-wide">
                <graphic id="eg3106" filename="../figeg3/EG3106.webp" type="webp"/>
                <caption>FIGURE 2.22.</caption>
                <calloutgroup>
                    <callout1>1. Impeller Wheel</callout1>
                    <callout1>2. Compressor Housing Backplate</callout1>
                    <callout1>3. Turbine Wheel</callout1>
                </calloutgroup>
            </figure>
        </step1>
    </svcproc>
